summary: It’d be neat to see Youtubers react to their TvTropes pages.
title: It’d be neat to see Youtubers react to their TvTropes pages.
body:
TVTropes compiles lists of different plot devices/character types etc found in multiple media and describes them/analyzes them.

For example: Both Buffy the Vampire Slayer and Harry Potter fit the trope “the Chosen One” 

Youtubers have TVTropes Pages too, listing fiction tropes that they are said to fit and it’s quite interesting and surprising at times too.

summary: When your best friend is saying some crazy shit
title: When your best friend is saying some crazy shit
body:
But you love them and the way they think, so all you can do is laugh and pull a Jim from The Office.

The thing is, there’s never any malice. Look at Dan’s expression in the last image. 

He’s so fond of Phil. Like, Phil is literally explaining how he would use a statue to attract a scorpion and then kill it. Phil’s mind works in a way we can’t understand, and Dan is so entertained and amused by it.

Their friendship is so pure <3

summary: I ALMOST FORGOT OMG OKAY So I made my brother (he’s 20 and bi and typically has a sick sense of humor) watch Dan’s diss track...
body:
I ALMOST FORGOT OMG OKAY So I made my brother (he’s 20 and bi and typically has a sick sense of humor) watch Dan’s diss track last night and his comments were:

“You look like a noodle?! Solid lyric.”

“Hehe posh voice. At least he knows.”

“Winnie the Pooh and Slenderman?? I ship it.”

“Okay um rhyming “Evan P” to “sexuality” is questionable but….”

*bursts of giggles throughout literally the whole thing*

“Secretly a furry… ummmm okay- I don’t think he’s kidding, though.”

“Okay well that was actually not the worst thing. I mean. It was pretty funny. Some of the rhymes were just a stretch but overall it was funny. And plus he’s hot, which definitely doesn’t hurt.”

And when I asked for his score out of 10, he said “I’d give it a solid 8. It was worth that much for sure.”


Keep in mind my brother has literally never watched a single Dan or Phil video in his life so this was all his observations in seeing only this video. I’m honestly not complaining but like 😭😭😂 I think I’ve converted a new member of the Phandom 💁🏻‍♀️
